Provides a version of Woddish's excellent Tiny Tank Fancy Howitzer that has had the dozer blade removed as an alternate option. Also contains parts that are enabled to be quickly swapped and edited for customization by changing visibility of components between different options for hatches, crew, symbols/icons.

This is intended for designers and modelers to product their own faction customized vehicles from in a standardized and high quality form.

Leverages Orcstain's excellent astartes symbols and bolter from Lord Chronos. Crew figure based on a DangItBlobby jarhead with parts from Daffmakes.

New part contributions are welcome!

If you like what I did and want to leave a tip it would be appreciated.

EDIT* It was pointed out to me that I had denied the tiny soldiers access to tiny rocket launchers. And that just wasn't right. New variants uploaded with multiple tiny rocket launchers to launch tiny rockets at your tiny foes! Because who loves ya, baby?! Tiny Tanks loves you!!!

Tiny Tanks are back baby! And they're speeding onto the tiny scene at a relatively high rate of pace! These tiny cavalry tanks are the perfect choice for the tiny soldier who wants to go fast! Flank, fix, and finish your tiny enemies with these little death dealers.
Comes in three distinct flavors, discover your favourite today!

Tiny tanks! The perfect thing to give a sense of scale to your tiny titans, tiny aircraft, or tiny anything! Add them as base decoration, add them as terrain decoration, create tiny war dioramas, do whatever you want with them! Anything is made better with the addition of tiny tanks.

Tiny tanks are intended for resin printers.
